productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Julisa has one of these. She works as a bartender and she says it looks crooked.
My co-worker Ali has one of these. He says it looks towering.
My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 15 gram!!!
